<p>Flipkart hosts Big Saving Days sale every few months. During the last Big Saving Days sale, the e-commerce giant sold several Apple products like iPhone XR, iPhone SE (2020), and other Android smartphones at lower prices. Other products like laptops, wireless accessories, and more were also available on sale.</p>

